    mct "Apa yang perlu aku katakan di sini?"

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:128
translate malay d20s03_2733996e:

    # mc "We're two friends, who can talk about things. And say whatever comes to our minds. And we had some great experiences together too."
    mc "Kita dua kawan, yang boleh bercakap tentang sesuatu. Dan katakan apa sahaja yang terlintas di fikiran kita. Dan kita juga ada beberapa pengalaman hebat bersama."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:130
translate malay d20s03_548c9123:

    # kb "Yeah. Like when you saw me spying on Chloe, and didn't say anything."
    kb "Yeah. Seperti ketika kau tengok aku mengintip Chloe, dan tak berkata apa-apa."
    
# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:131
translate malay d20s03_86c38a57:

    # kb "Took a nasty fall."
    kb "Terjatuh teruk."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:132
translate malay d20s03_82f74230:

    # kb "And you didn't make any judgments about me at the cafe."
    kb "Dan kau tak membuat sebarang penilaian tentang aku di kafe."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:135
translate malay d20s03_c5d73ad2:

    # kb "Or the fun we had at the party."
    kb "Atau keseronokan yang kita ada di parti itu."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:136
translate malay d20s03_24c661b2:

    # kb "And when you chose to satisfy our desires... I know you don't think much of me, but really, I'm thankful."
    kb "Dan bila kau memilih untuk memuaskan keinginan kami... aku tahu kau tak terlalu memikirkan aku, tapi sebenarnya, aku bersyukur."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:138
translate malay d20s03_0d4c935a:

    # kb "Well, actually, I don't remember much of the events that happened lately."
    kb "Sebenarnya, aku tak ingat banyak peristiwa yang berlaku kebelakangan ini."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:139
translate malay d20s03_d26b9e33:

    # kb "That's a lie, I'm just choosing to forget."
    kb "Itu bohong, aku hanya memilih untuk melupakan."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:140
translate malay d20s03_62531da2:

    # kb "But if memories are all we have, then, doesn't that mean we're just living in the past? That there's nowhere for this to go?"
    kb "Tapi jika hanya kenangan yang kita ada, bukankah itu bermakna kita hanya hidup di masa lalu? Tak ada tempat untuk ini untuk pergi?"

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:142
translate malay d20s03_eb19af2d:

    # mc "I'm not sure."
    mc "Aku tak pasti."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:143
translate malay d20s03_96c851b6:

    # mct "Okay, there's something wrong for sure. I need to make an excuse and {i}leave{/i}."
    mct "Okay, pasti ada sesuatu yang tak kena. Aku kena buat alasan dan {i}pergi{/i}."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:145
translate malay d20s03_92d5de5d:

    # kb "You know, I was so glad when I heard you were taking this class."
    kb "Aku tahu, aku sangat gembira bila aku dengar kau mengikuti kelas ini."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:146
translate malay d20s03_f44ee7f7:

    # kb "There's a reason you don't see me with other people that often."
    kb "Ada sebab kau tak nampak aku dengan orang lain begitu kerap."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:147
translate malay d20s03_db948228:

    # kb "You might be thinking I was with Chloe the whole time. But we don't always get along, you know."
    kb "Kau mungkin fikir aku bersama Chloe sepanjang masa. Tapi kami tak selalu serasi, kau tahu."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:149
translate malay d20s03_7502dc42:

    # mc "Yeah, I know."
    mc "Yeah, aku tahu."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:150
translate malay d20s03_91e7fe9e:

    # mc "I'm wondering. Where is this all coming from?"
    mc "Aku tertanya-tanya. Dari mana datangnya semua ini?"

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:151
translate malay d20s03_d070cdab:

    # mc "What's bringing this on?"
    mc "Apa yang menyebabkan ini?"

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:153
translate malay d20s03_18dca563:

    # kb "Well, you know I told you, I started a new job not too long ago."
    kb "Aku ada beritahu kau, aku dah mula kerja baru tak lama dulu."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:154
translate malay d20s03_ec3731e3:

    # kb "It sucks. It takes up all my time. And I got passed over for a promotion."
    kb "Memang payah. Ia mengambil semua masa aku. Dan aku dilepaskan untuk kenaikan pangkat."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:155
translate malay d20s03_3e9e4762:

    # kb "Studying sucks. Life sucks."
    kb "Belajar payah. Hidup pun payah."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:157
translate malay d20s03_ae7de870:

    # mc "That's not true."
    mc "Itu tak betul."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:158
translate malay d20s03_58e6bd3e:

    # kb "It is. [mcname], you're surrounded by how many women?"
    kb "Ianya betul. [mcname], kau dikelilingi oleh berapa ramai wanita?"

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:160
translate malay d20s03_3634247a:

    # kb "You're living the dream, and I'm... well, I'm still here."
    kb "Kau jalani hidup kau dengan imipian yang hampir semua lelaki ada, dan aku... baik, aku masih di sini."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:161
translate malay d20s03_c677bbd7:

    # kb "Feels like I didn't change much."
    kb "Rasayan aku tak banyak berubah."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:163
translate malay d20s03_5f74651f:

    # mc "That's not true. I have my difficulties too. I'm sure I'm not the only one nervous about this upcoming test..."
    mc "Itu tak benar. Aku pun ada susah senang juga. Aku pasti bukan aku sahaja yang gementar dengan ujian yang akan datang ini..."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:164
translate malay d20s03_2346bbd1:

    # mc "And for the record... I like you."
    mc "Dan untuk rekod... aku suka kau."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:166
translate malay d20s03_3cdd043a:

    # kb "Oh no bro, are you confessing something..."
    kb "Oh tak bro, kau mengaku sesuatu..."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:168
translate malay d20s03_6ada18e2:

    # mc "As a friend! As a friend."
    mc "Sebagai kawan! Sebagai kawan."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:170
translate malay d20s03_5a020e24:

    # mc "And your sister likes you too. That's the point. You're not alone."
    mc "Dan adik kau pun sukakan kau. Itulah hakikatnya. Kau tak keseorangan."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:172
translate malay d20s03_730b8bb9:

    # mc "And your girlfriend likes you too. That's the point. You're not alone."
    mc "Dan teman wanita kau juga sukakan kau. Itulah hakikatnya. Kau tak keseorangan."

