translate malay d20s03_7868a094:

    # mc "A lot of people will judge you, call you names, whatever. As long as you're happy, isn't that what matters?"
    mc "Ramai orang akan menilai kau, memanggil kau nama, apa sahaja. Asalkan kau bahagia, bukankah itu yang penting?"

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:175
translate malay d20s03_2b62f101:

    # kb "Thanks. I know."
    kb "Terima kasih. Aku tahu."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:176
translate malay d20s03_69d04d33:

    # kb "I've done a lot of thinking, a lot of growing up. I still have a long way to go, but I feel like I'm hitting a huge milestone in my life."
    kb "Aku dah lakukan banyak pemikiran, banyak masa membesar. Masih ada perjalanan yang jauh, tapi aku rasa aku sedang mencapai satu kejayaan besar dalam hidup aku."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:177
translate malay d20s03_87754725:

    # mc "Okay, Kevin."
    mc "Okay, Kevin."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:179
translate malay d20s03_341fdde5:

    # kb "I kinda made a decision, and I don't know what I want to do. But I need you to do me a favor."
    kb "Aku mungkin membuat keputusan dan aku tak tahu apa yang aku lakukan. Tapi aku perlukan kau untuk membantu aku."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:180
translate malay d20s03_9571ac14:

    # kb "For a long time, I felt unhappy."
    kb "Untuk masa yang lama, aku berasa tdak gembira."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:181
translate malay d20s03_55a4d2ec:

    # kb "I know I've been chill with you, but you know. How would I share this type of heavy news?"
    kb "Aku tahu aku pernah bersikap dingin dengan kau, tapi kau tahu. Macam mana aku nak kongsi berita berat ini?"

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:183
translate malay d20s03_53806588:

    # kb "I tried to, but there just wasn't too much time these days."
    kb "Aku cuba, tapi tak ada masa yang terlalu banyak hari ini."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:184
translate malay d20s03_709bc3ad:

    # kb "I don't feel like I belong here. And so I'm going away."
    kb "Aku tak rasa aku sepatutnya berada di sini. Jadi aku akan pergi."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:185
translate malay d20s03_be6fa98b:

    # mc "Going away? Going where? I just got here!"
    mc "Pergi? Pergi mana? Aku baru sampai!"

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:187
translate malay d20s03_771f9583:

    # kb "Haha. Not at this immediate moment."
    kb "Haha. Bukan pada masa ini."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:188
translate malay d20s03_b277a9a8:

    # kb "Sorry. This is a little out of left field, I know. It's been an overwhelming experience."
    kb "Maaf. Ini agak pelik, aku tahu. Ia merupakan pengalaman yang amat menggembirakan."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:189
translate malay d20s03_1e00fc7d:

    # kb "Feels like we've known each other all our lives. And now it's all going to change."
    kb "Rasanya kita dah mengenali antara satu sama lain sepanjang hidup kita. Dan kini semuanya akan berubah."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:191
translate malay d20s03_c84eb5c7:

    # kb "Everything changed for us when Fetish Locator dropped into our laps."
    kb "Semuanya berubah untuk kita apabila Fetish Locator jatuh ke pangkuan kita."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:192
translate malay d20s03_a3cd034f:

    # kb "It's been a blessing and a curse."
    kb "Ia adalah rahmat dan kutukan. Ia adalah yang terbaik dan lebih teruk."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:193
translate malay d20s03_fa5f14e7:

    # mc "Definitely. Crazy couple of weeks."
    mc "Mestilah. Dua minggu ini memamng gila."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:195
translate malay d20s03_76105528:

    # kb "So about that favor."
    kb "Jadi tentang itu."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:196
translate malay d20s03_3f871f46:

    # mc "Hmm?"
    mc "Hmm?"

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:198
translate malay d20s03_a8c4d259:

    # kb "We made a decision, that we were going to go away and elope. Get married. Screw what our parents want. We only have one life to live, right?"
    kb "Kami buat keputusan, yang kami akan pergi dan kawin lari.  Pergi mampuslah apa yang ibu bapa kami nak. Kami hanya mempunyai satu nyawa untuk hidup, kan?"

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:199
translate malay d20s03_a3b1a71e:

    # mc "I guess."
    mc "Rasanya."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:200
translate malay d20s03_59ec00a0:

    # kb "When the time comes for you, and you have to make a no-win decision, I'm sure you'll be braver than me."
    kb "Apabila tiba masanya untuk kau, dan kau perlu membuat keputusan tanpa menang, aku pasti kau akan lebih berani daripada aku."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:202
translate malay d20s03_53cf85a0:

    # kb "Stick around, face the consequences."
    kb "Tetaplah, hadapi akibatnya."

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:203
translate malay d20s03_f4b72fa4:

    # kb "Because I'm going to go away. Maybe you'll join me?"
    kb "Kerana aku akan pergi. Mungkin kau akan sertai aku?"

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:204
translate malay d20s03_2ffde6f3:

    # mc "I don't think that'll be necessary. I mean, aren't you going to stay until after the exam, at least?"
    mc "Aku rasa itu tak perlu. Maksud aku, takkah kau akan tunggu sehingga selepas peperiksaan, sekurang-kurangnya?"

# game/code/d20/d20s03.rpy:206
translate malay d20s03_a5f3f6ef:

